Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.89,0:01:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}中國公司或承建長島跨海大橋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊芙琳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Evelyn...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-丹頓先生  -叫我雷米就行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Mr. Danton. - Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你最近怎樣  -我還行  挺不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- How are you? - I'm OK. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好久不見  -是啊  有段時間了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Been awhile. - Yeah, it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-早上好  -副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Good morning. - Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懷特豪爾酋長\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Chief Whitehall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德魯·傑克遜也要參加會面嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is Andrew Jackson going to be joining us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs16\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美國第七任總統  曾在1812年戰爭中與印第安人血戰  得號"印第安人殺手"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  這是嚴重的疏忽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I'm sorry, that's a terrible oversight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格  麻煩你  把畫像拿走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Doug, will you... remove that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.33,0:02:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們先照相吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why don't we take the photograph first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.24,0:02:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位請坐\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們談談聯邦認證吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's talk federal recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想必貴部落已經等待許久了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your tribe has waited long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-哪位  -是我  麗薩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Who is it? - It's me. It's Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能進去嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要做些臨時工\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Temp jobs, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文職工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Clerical work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼下我在一個牙醫診所兼職\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Right now I'm doing part-time at a dentist's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接待員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是大材小用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You deserve better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就只能將就了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都好久沒進星巴克了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is the first time I've had Starbucks since I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今這對我而言是種奢侈了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a luxury for me these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許格蘭頓-希爾能提供你一個職位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe there's something for you at Glendon Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's nice of you to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但只怕那樣的公司我做不來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I'm not the right fit for a place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當然能\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sure you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.79,0:04:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在非盈利領域工作20年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Twenty years' experience in the non-profit sphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也經常和非政府組織協作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we coordinated all the time NGOs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的經驗對我們會很有價值\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you'd be a valuable asset to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-克萊爾當初就不該解僱你  -可不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Claire should've never let you go. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是不說了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well... I'll hold my tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.14,0:04:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和她現在也不聯繫了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She and I don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們鬧僵了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We had a falling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.68,0:04:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她不是個忠誠的人  -的確不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Loyalty isn't her thing. - No, it is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看她不會忠於任何人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't think she's loyal to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-也許除了她丈夫吧  -也許吧  也難說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Except maybe her husband. - Maybe... maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不確定  但是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing I know for certain, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.81,0:04:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和一個人共事那麼久...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...spend a decade working for someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她威脅你了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She threaten you or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  她只是不肯走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. She just wouldn't leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.67,0:04:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不想報警\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not like I wanted to call the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也不是壞人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, no, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:05:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我試著和她談  但她又開始抽了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I tried to talk to her. Then she lit up a pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-冰毒  -是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Meth? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們做室友時整天吸那個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When we were roommates that's all it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經難以自拔\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I used to be really deep into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有海洛因\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Heroin, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到我加入了友誼會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And then I found the fellowship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能幫你什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  我不該\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I shouldn't --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我很高興你來找我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I'm glad you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你上班要遲到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know you're late for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就請病假\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll call in sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  我沒事  我這就走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't do that. It's fine. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說  別回去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean, don't go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣行嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你鑰匙  方便你進出\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Keys. In case you need to come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我大約七點半回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be back around 7:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你用不著謝我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't have to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}瑞秋·波斯納  有個朋友要來我這兒暫住幾天  不用擔心\N她只是要找個地方住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只要總統一個電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All the President has to do is pick up the phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大橋就能批下來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and the bridge is approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果總統想參與這事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the President had wanted to be involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他早就打電話了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}he would have already made that call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.44,0:06:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是他的提議  琳達\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's his initiative, Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾經是  但現在貿易戰已經打響了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Was his initiative. We're in a trade war now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也用不著把好端端的政策全丟掉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But that doesn't mean we have to abandon good policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這會與他現在的立場不一致\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's inconsistent with his current stance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外資投資管理委員會有30天的時間批准開建\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The Committee on Foreign Investment has 30 days to approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在只剩六天了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's only six days left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有美國總統的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They won't act without a directive
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接指示  他們絕不會批准的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}from the President of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.10,0:06:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白  你一直堅定支援對中國\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm confused, you've been the biggest proponent
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,採取強硬態度\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}of a strong position against China.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這話可不對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That is not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早先的建議與此相反\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I advocated the opposite early on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎很在乎這座橋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You seem fixated on this bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的原因嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is something else going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失業率達到9.2%\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Unemployment is at nine-point-two,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通貨膨脹率飆升\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}inflation is skyrocketing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上就要丟掉多數席位了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we're on the verge of losing our majority.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統需要一則好訊息向世人公佈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The president needs to offer a piece of good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一座橋  簡直是微不足道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A bridge? That's a drop in the bucket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.09,0:06:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作  基礎設施\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jobs, infrastructure,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.51,0:06:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,削減赤字\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}deficit reduction--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是沒說實話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're still not being straight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒別的用心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have no ulterior motive here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你非要這麼想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but if you feel that strongly
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統也非要這麼想的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and the president feels that strongly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不管了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}then I'll back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.07,0:06:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會再提了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't mention it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這的確是個明智的決定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think that's a wise decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們該團結起來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We should be a united front.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.15,0:07:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常贊同\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I couldn't agree more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼凡事都這麼不容易\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why does everything have to be a struggle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就沒人能說一次"好"嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can't some people just say "Yes" for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要總統明後天的日程表\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need the president's schedule for the next two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她改變主意了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She change her mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們下一步做什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So what's our next move?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去辦橋的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll focus on the bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去跟印第安人事務部談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you talk to the Indian affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懷特豪爾的部落越早得到認證\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The sooner that Whitehall's tribe gets recognized,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賭場就能越早動工\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the sooner they can break ground on that casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許這對我有幫助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe it will help me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多公開談談那事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I talk about it more in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像在你的訪談上那樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean that's what your interview did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打進電話  公開說出那些事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When I called. When I could say those things out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.32,0:07:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不想讓你覺得你有義務如此\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, we don't want you to feel obligated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道媒體還一直纏著你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know the press hasn't left you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們還要繼續給我拍照\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If they're going to keep taking pictures of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我至少該說點什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I should at least say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥金尼斯上軍事法庭指日可待\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, that's only going to become more intense
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事態會越來越緊張\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when McGinnis gets closer to his court-marshal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我準備好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.56,0:07:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能去跟三軍委員會談談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you come and speak to the Armed Services Committee,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說出你的往事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}tell your story,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼法案一定能進入投票階段\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I feel confident we can get it to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的重磅新聞他們不能無視\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd be too much coverage to ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得法案會通過嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you think it will pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要先要通過委員會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to get it through committee first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我要說明  梅根\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But let's be clear, Megan,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.77,0:08:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不光要舉證\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it's not just the testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍後你還得面對媒體\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll need you to do a media avail after.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍照片  做聲明\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Photo ops, a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好的  -你不是一個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Ok. - You won't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直支援你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be standing right next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And so will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這樣做對嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you think we're doing the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她拉到鏡頭前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hauling her in front of the cameras?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說她想這樣做  我們得相信她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have to trust her when she says she wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但重要的是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it's very important
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是你  白宮也支援我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that the White House backs us up on this, not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不確定加勒特會不會公開表示支援\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure if Garrett will get involved publicly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能和他談談嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, can you talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們最近沒怎麼交談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We haven't been doing much talking about anything lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情況還沒好轉嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Things haven't gotten any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們差不多一個禮拜沒說過話了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We haven't said a word to each other in almost a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也經歷過  真可怕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've been there, it's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和弗蘭克嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}With Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是怎麼做的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們找了一個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We saw someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是指心理諮詢師嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You mean a therapist?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不擔心被曝光嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Weren't you worried about exposure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個牧師\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He was a minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚴格說  他不是心理諮詢師\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He wasn't exactly a therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更像是精神指引那種的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was more like a spiritual guidance, type thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的區別是他有學位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The only difference was that he had a degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以幫你聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I could put you in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太冒險了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.71,0:09:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是個建議而已\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是改變主意就告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me know if you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你能試著和加勒特談談嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In the meantime, can you try to talk to Garrett?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們非常需要他的支援\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We really need his support with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請帶他進來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Show him in, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼正式\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請坐吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you have a seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不該讓實習生工作到這麼晚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Shouldn't keep your interns so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也許沒有個人生活  但他們有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You and I might not have lives, but they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有工作沒做完就要繼續做  這他們懂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When there's work to be done, we work. They know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.08,0:10:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼晚上10點叫我過來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why am I here at 10 at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共和黨的錢從哪來的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where is the GOP getting their money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是問那兩千五百萬吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That is a $25 million question, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You must have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會那麼認為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你無所不知\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because you know things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以格蘭頓-希爾升你做合夥人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's why Glendon Hill made you partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們大部分客戶都是民主黨人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Most of our clients are Democrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你一樣毫不知情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm just as much in the dark as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要失去我的選區了  雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm losing in my district, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我能幫你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I wish I could help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我贏得選舉  也無所謂了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Even if I pull off a win, it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共和黨佔據眾議院多數席位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The GOP takes the House,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會被踢出領導層\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I lose my spot in the leadership,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去職務  失去我為之努力的一切\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}this office, everything I've worked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我替你難過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I feel for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你想要的是我不知道的資訊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you want information i don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們上次的見面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you upset
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你不高興了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}about the last time we saw each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的很清楚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I made myself clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能談談嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不談工作  不談政治\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No work, no politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想談什麼都可以\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can talk about whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.74,0:11:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟人約會  從未超過六個月\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've never... been with anyone for more than six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在軍隊的時候  總是四處奔波\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When I was in the army I was always on the move and, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.81,0:11:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入國會之後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Since I've been in Congress,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又實在沒有時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just haven't had time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是要你嫁給我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wasn't asking to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是想比一夜情更認真一些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just to be more than company for a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.44,0:11:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你依然那麼想嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you still want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來了  不是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm here, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們必須劃定一個界限\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There would have to be clear boundaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們私底下的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever we have privately
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能影響我們的公事關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}couldn't affect our professional relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就不該在你的辦公室談這些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then we shouldn't be having this conversation in your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很高興我們能把話說開\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm glad we had this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你還想見我  給我打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you'd like to have another, just call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以省掉祕書這一關\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can leave the secretaries out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會再看看  讓琳達聯繫你們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll review this and have Linda get in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-謝謝  先生  -謝謝  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Thank you, sir. - Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good morning, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hi, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把波本威士忌放在家裡了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I left my bourbon at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你有時間喝個咖啡嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but you have time for some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用  你自便\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm fine, you go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想跟你談談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wanted to talk to you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑斐遜港大橋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}about the Port Jefferson Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達說你們倆談過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Linda told me you two spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你重新考慮過嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you reconsidered?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在時機不對  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not the right time, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到緊張局勢過去後\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll find some other project
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們再找別的項目展示我們的計劃\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to showcase our program once tensions subside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在競選中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}During the campaign,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你反覆承諾會重視重要的基建\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you repeatedly promised to address critical infrastructure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經進入了你任期的第二個年頭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're well into your second year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.27,0:13:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個項目已經蓄勢待發\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This project is ready to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不想再重頭搞一個吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you don't want to have to start from square one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想中期選舉的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm thinking midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得表現出一致性\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have to project consistency.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但人們不會為了一致性投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Except people don't vote for consistency,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.59,0:13:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們只為確實的進展投票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}they vote for concrete progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達說你似乎對這座橋很執迷\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Linda mentioned that you seemed obsessed with this bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在覺得她說對了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm beginning to think she was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個背後捅刀的噁心婊子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The backstabbing, vomit-inducing bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她說對了嗎  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is she right, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說說你為什麼這麼在乎這座橋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me why this bridge is so important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.23,0:13:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓你受影響\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wanted to insulate you from this--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受什麼影響\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我與中國人私下接觸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You asked me to back channel with the Chinese
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就繼續那麼做了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and I have continued to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我讓你停止跟中國人私下接觸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I told you to stop back channeling
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:13:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你還是那麼做了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you did anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不告訴我  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Without informing me, Frank--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得拉開你的距離\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I needed to distance you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些事是不能讓總統知道的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There are issues that a president cannot be aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.39,0:14:06.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What issues--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我能告訴你的是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But, what I can tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大橋的建設\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...is that the building of this bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以直接影響我們在中期選舉中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}directly affects our ability to combat the Republicans
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與共和黨的對抗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}in the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中國人是不是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have the Chinese--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生  你正在問\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President, you are asking questions
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想知道答案的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you do not want the answers to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的風險有多大  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right, how much danger are we in, Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們現在就結束談話  就沒有風險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}None if we end this conversation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.71,0:14:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時候我覺得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sometimes I feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經無法控制我自己的政府了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm losing control over my goddamn administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你承受著很大壓力  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're under pressure, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你並沒有失控\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but you're not losing control.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多人在幫你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have people who are looking out for you:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我  琳達  你妻子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}me, Linda, your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對她也快失去控制了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I might be losing control of her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該這麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I shouldn't have said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然她也是為我著想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course she wants the best for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾說了什麼嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Has Claire said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她們有聊天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know they talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not much...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是說你們之間有點磕磕絆絆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}just that things have been a little rocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是說得太輕了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, that's an understatement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作是世界上最難做的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have the most difficult job on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換了誰婚姻上都會出現問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It would take a toll on any marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我勸你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which is why I'm urging you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新考慮一下橋的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to reconsider your decision on the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這話不是以副總統的身份\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I'd say that not as your vice president...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是以你朋友的身份\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but as your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我在乎你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because I care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我會再看看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right, I'll... I'll have another look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  總...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  加勒特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗羅斯特先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Frost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}內務部  印第安人事務局
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們2006年就提交了所有檔案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We filed all our paperwork back in 2006.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.97,0:15:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事無鉅細\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We dotted all of our I's
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該做得都做了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and crossed all of our T's.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有超過317份申請\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's over 317 applications.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每一份申請最少需要一年去評估\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Each one requires at least a year to review.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你需要多僱些調查員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You need more researchers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是人事的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not just personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要考慮出行  歸檔  行政工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's travel, filing, administration...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.75,0:16:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出個價吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Name the figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一千二  三百萬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Twelve, thirteen million.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這需要國會的撥款\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That requires an appropriation from Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統會搞定的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The vice president can make that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但首先你得認證尤幹亞部落\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But first we need you to recognize the Ugaya tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們規定  要分先來後到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Our policy is first come, first serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的申請我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There are other applications which we--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼爾·拉尼根把我們踢出部落了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Daniel Lanagin disenrolled us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們失去了印第安人事務局的福利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We lost our right to BIA benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.49,0:16:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不單只是要開賭場吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is this more about starting a casino?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了討回公道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's about correcting an injustice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能牽扯到部落糾紛中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't be getting involved in inner-tribal conflicts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想要那筆撥款\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you want that appropriation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個月\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果歷史核查沒問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe less if all the ancestry holds up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉尼根知道了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lanagin knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And what did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想見面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He wants to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這次是去他的地盤\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But on his turf this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想個法子  讓我能去密蘇里\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need a way to get to Missouri
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.82,0:16:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不引人注意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}without attracting any attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏麥克的選區在堪薩斯城\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Womack's district's in Kansas City.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離賭場不遠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not far from the casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看他最近有什麼活動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}See if he has any events coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集會  慈善募捐之類的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Rallies, fundraisers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:16:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾法案的聯署人找得怎麼樣了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How's it coming with co-sponsors for Claire's bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常好  進展很大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Terrific. We're making great progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一篇演講  讓國會明白\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One speech. It'll send a message to Congress that --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也要讓參謀長聯席會議知道我要踐踏他們...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And a message to the Joint Chiefs that I'm trampling on--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年有兩萬四千起性侵事件\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Twenty-four thousand assaults last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.35,0:17:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有三千起上報\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}only 3,000 reported because--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.56,0:17:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道是什麼情況\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know the figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道多少人因為創傷而自殺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you know how many suicides result from the trauma--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是資料的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not the question of statistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這部法案能挽救生命\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This bill will save lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能晚點再說嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can we discuss this later?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次會面還是我預約的呢  加勒特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had to schedule this meeting, Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在大中午的  特莉莎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's the middle of the day, Tricia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.56,0:17:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你十分清楚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別逼我回家再遊說你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't make me lobby you when I go home--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉打擾了  總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry to interrupt, Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祕書長到了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The secretary general's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再給我兩分鐘\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I got two more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在12點30了  他約的是12點15\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's 12:30. He was scheduled for 12:15.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.88,0:17:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該挽留我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You were supposed to tell me to stay,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很高興我至少還值兩分鐘\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but it's nice to know I'm worth at least two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  特莉莎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hi, Tricia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, please, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太糟了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, that's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  當然\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找找他的電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me grab his number for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.14,0:18:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫托馬斯·拉金博士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His name is Dr. Thomas Larkin,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,號碼是2022516258\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}at 202-251-6258.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想的話  我可以提前和他聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if you'd like, I can give him a call beforehand
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他知道你要去找他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and let him know you'll be reaching out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  有什麼我能幫忙的儘管開口\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay. Well you let me know if I can be of any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安  特莉莎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good night, Tricia.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.62,0:18:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等著瞧吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的主旨是將色原說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The idea is to take color theory
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,徹底顛覆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and turn it on its head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打破所有陳規\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Break all the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是精彩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說你的客戶是誰來著\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who'd you say your client is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒說過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想沒準我認識他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was just wondering if maybe I knew them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不認識\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫且說他是個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's say he's a collector
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四處發掘新人才的收藏家吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}always on the lookout for new talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為亞當·嘉樂威工作  對嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I understand you work for Adam Galloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能掙些生活費\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it's a way to pay the bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你喜歡那種風格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean, Adam's a good photographer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞當的確是個優秀的攝影師\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if you like that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我則對形態更感興趣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm much more interested in form.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些加起來多少錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How much for all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全買了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to buy them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}副總統親臨堪薩斯城  安德伍德將在烏麥克籌款會上發表演講
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密蘇里州的"不輕信州"外號可不是白叫的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Missouri is the Show Me State for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正要向全國人民證明\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And we need to show the rest of America
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的領導層堅實可靠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that we can keep our leadership intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.51,0:19:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看見滿屋賓朋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It is a pleasure to look out
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人人喜笑顏開  我很高興\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and see a room full of smiling faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這場面在華盛頓特區可不是天天都能見到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not something you see every day in Washington, D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的編輯怎麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What did your editors say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五千字\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}5,000 words.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.21,0:19:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起碼應該翻倍啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This should be twice that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:19:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能爭取到八千字\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can probably get them to eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我還要採訪第一夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I'm gonna need the first lady, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,單獨採訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Separate interviews.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我和安德伍德先生商量一下\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let me talk to Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.81,0:20:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How come you're coming to me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是康納來和我談這事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with this instead of Connor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.71,0:20:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你別跟別人說  他辭職了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Between you and me, he's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳槽去太空探索技術公司了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He got a job at SpaceX.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他自願的還是被人逼走的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His choice or was he pushed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般人不喜歡和我共事  馬特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}People don't like working with me, Matt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你大約是絕無僅有的一個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You may be the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不喜歡和你打交道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't like you either.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果能採訪到第一夫人  我或許會喜歡你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I might if you give me the First Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們明天要跟三軍委員會面談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They'll both be speaking to armed services tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.89,0:20:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有梅根·漢納希\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Along with Megan Hennessy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.13,0:20:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就是那個被將軍...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's the one the general--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給你安排單獨專訪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll set up a one-on-one,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡訊溝通你的報道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}text you for your piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.69,0:20:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  等你訊息了  老兄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right, let me know, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意為《時代》效勞  夥計\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anything for the Times, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為《時代》效勞  是吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anything for the Times, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻把我們擋在捐助者會議大門外\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then we get shut out of donor meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.82,0:20:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說的是雜誌  沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The magazine. And yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德·塔斯克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你老闆去年十月和這人見過面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your boss went to see him last October.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都記在國會的旅行報告裡了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's in his congressional travel report.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.37,0:20:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當時我還沒來工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Before my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說過他們倆從沒見過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said they didn't communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.56,0:20:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的原話是"據我瞭解不認識"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I said, "Not to my knowledge."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在就在密蘇里\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're in Missouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是捐助者之一\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's not one of the donors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能引述你的話嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can quote you on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別把我的名字拼錯了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you spell my name right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般來講  我不引述北方作家的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, normally, I don't quote Northern writers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有時候他們中也有人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but every now and then one of them says something
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能說出挺有道理的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that makes a lot of sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位叫愛默生的老兄  你們沒準聽說過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and this Emerson fellow you probably heard of,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:21:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他曾經說  交友的唯一辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}once wrote that the only way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是自己夠朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to have a friend is to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想各位非常清楚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think you all know
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰瑞對他的選區人民有多夠朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}what kind of a friend Terry has been to this district.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天  我驕傲地向各位介紹他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So I am proud to introduce him today
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並稱他為我的朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and to call him my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在有請\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you please welcome,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.84,0:21:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多數黨領袖\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the majority leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰瑞·烏麥克眾議員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Representative Terry Womack.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都安排好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We all set?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.69,0:21:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴媒體\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I told the press
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.32,0:21:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你將和幾位捐助者私下會面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you were having some private meetings with contributors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人質疑嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Any protests?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.20,0:21:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  除了艾拉·薩伊德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're good except for Ayala Sayyad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  她怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是個盲點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Potential blind spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往車那邊走  邊走邊說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell me on the way to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許亂叫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Calm down. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是愉快的巧遇啊  雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What a pleasant surprise, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.34,0:22:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為今天要和你單獨見面呢  丹尼爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was expecting to see you privately today, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事關重大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a serious matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我把"酋長"都請來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I invite all the chiefs to the circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泳池不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nice pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.46,0:22:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒在裡面遊過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've never swum in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.25,0:22:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氯水弄得我眼睛疼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The chlorine hurts my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想遊的話  歡迎試水\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're welcome to take a dip in it if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.28,0:22:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.42,0:22:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德跟我說你喜歡吃肋排\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, Raymond tells me you're a ribs man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這兒有三份頂級的肉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I've got three of the choicest pieces of meat
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這輩子難得一嘗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you'll ever see in your life coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對不會想錯過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You do not want to pass on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.69,0:23:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會待很久\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't be here long.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.58,0:23:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,言歸正傳  尤幹亞群體\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So, the Ugaya band.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰山一角\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tip of the iceberg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不是正式的部落\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're not a real tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們就要成為正式的了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're about to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.54,0:23:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  他們是一群製造麻煩的傢伙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, they're a bunch of troublemakers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是報太大希望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with too much hope on their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他們得到認證\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Once they get recognized,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.18,0:23:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能建立自己的賭場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}they're gonna have their own casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最快也要兩年吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In two years... at best?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁著還有泳池好好享受吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You better enjoy this pool while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.54,0:23:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你的賭場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't think your casino
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.58,0:23:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承受不住那麼激烈的競爭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}can stand that sort of competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為懷特豪爾一離開印第安人事務局\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who do you think Whitehall called
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.59,0:23:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最先給誰打了電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as soon as he left the BIA?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.35,0:23:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你承諾兩年後給他們賭場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You offer them a casino two years from now,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.80,0:23:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我們能給他真正想要的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we offered what they really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迴歸我的部落\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Reenrollment in my tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.93,0:23:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的冰山一角正在融化  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A tip of your iceberg is melting, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.26,0:23:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你時間也不多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you do not have time on your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣如何\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so how about this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幫我和加勒特重歸於好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You help me repair my relationship with Garrett,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.40,0:23:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹和我就讓資金\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dan and I here get the money
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.99,0:24:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流向正確的方向\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}flowing back in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣如何\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How about this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.91,0:24:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓印第安人事務局調查你們兩個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I get the BIA to investigate both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.71,0:24:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和馮的關係  洗錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Connection to Feng, laundering--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.36,0:24:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以  但你不會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You could, but you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.54,0:24:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不敢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't dare.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.91,0:24:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經資助民主黨九年了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My money has been going to the Democrats for nine years.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.18,0:24:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是他們的黨鞭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You were the whip for all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.70,0:24:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你指戳我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You implicate us,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.50,0:24:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己也自身難保\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you implicate yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.57,0:24:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還會殃及領導層的每個人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And everyone in the leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.43,0:24:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛排來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Here comes the steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.60,0:24:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會喜歡這個的  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now you are going to enjoy this, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.08,0:24:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.77,0:24:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.22,0:24:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚐嚐吧  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now dig in, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.08,0:24:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別喂蒼蠅了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Before the flies get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.26,0:24:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不用了  謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll pass, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.24,0:24:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你確定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.69,0:24:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是醬燒鬆阪牛肉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is soy-fed Matsusaka beef.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.16,0:24:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道  我的祖先會對這頭牛禱告\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know, my ancestors would've prayed to this heifer
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.83,0:24:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祭奠它的靈魂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to honor her spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.57,0:24:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是兩百塊一磅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But at 200 bucks a pound,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.73,0:24:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想  傳統還是滾邊吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I figure... fuck tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.97,0:24:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  及時行樂  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on, live a little, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.57,0:24:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要叫副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.96,0:24:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not my Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.98,0:25:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在是在自治區的領土上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're on sovereign land.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.43,0:25:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗可真好猜  不是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dogs are so predictable, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.32,0:25:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替我安排與沃克會面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Set up a meeting with Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.52,0:25:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以就今晚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tonight, if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.38,0:25:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我六點能到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I should be back by six.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.72,0:25:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉尼根沒讓步嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lanagin didn't budge?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.92,0:25:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他讓尤幹亞迴歸了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He reenrolled the Ugaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.11,0:25:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得馬上把橋的事敲定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have to get the bridge approved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.54,0:25:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去聯繫琳達\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll call Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.35,0:25:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繞開她  我不想讓她參與會面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bypass her, I don't want her in the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.31,0:25:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就去辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.26,0:25:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.01,0:25:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,密查姆  和飛機聯繫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Meechum, get in touch with the plane
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.19,0:25:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回程航班要做肋排\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}have them make ribs for the flight back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.35,0:25:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.27,0:27:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.98,0:27:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有空嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.74,0:27:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  總統要見我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, the President asked to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.07,0:27:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  他沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, he didn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.73,0:27:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你要求會面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you requested the meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.63,0:27:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後我取消了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and I took it off the schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.19,0:27:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幹了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You did what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.27,0:27:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去你辦公室聊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's go in your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.42,0:27:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你撒謊了  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You lied, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.47,0:27:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說橋的事你不管了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said you would let the bridge go
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.63,0:27:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後就揹著我搗鬼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and then you went behind my back,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.65,0:27:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這會兒就想這麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}just like you're trying to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.46,0:27:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要徵求你的同意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I do not require your permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.20,0:27:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  但你應該叫上我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, but you should involve me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.97,0:27:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統和副總統之間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The President and the Vice President
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.28,0:27:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題需要私下討論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}have issues they must discuss privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.23,0:27:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對我保密\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When you are secretive,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.09,0:27:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就做不好我的工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it prevents me from being able to do my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.25,0:27:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣把會面取消\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And when you cancel meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.34,0:27:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也讓我做不好我的工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it prevents me from being able to do mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.52,0:27:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想聊聊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which is why I wanted to talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.51,0:27:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才能解決問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so we can work things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.59,0:27:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我不想浪費時間  -我們應該合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- I will not waste my time - We should be working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.90,0:27:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,膨脹你的自尊心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}inflating your sense of self-importance!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.80,0:27:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.76,0:27:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你贏過多少次選舉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How many elections have you won?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.99,0:27:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當過多少個國會委員會的主席\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How many congressional committees have you chaired?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.29,0:27:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是我在競選時推薦了你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you even be working in the White House
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.60,0:27:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在會在白宮工作嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if I hadn't recommended you during the campaign?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.60,0:27:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一直在還你人情嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I returned that favor and then some.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.57,0:28:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你的辦公桌在哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look where your desk is now!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.23,0:28:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們就互不相欠了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I'd say we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.86,0:28:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要還想讓我尊重你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if you want to maintain my respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.81,0:28:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的做法大錯特錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you're going about it all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.17,0:28:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想跟你解決問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I asked you in here to work out a situation--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.55,0:28:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是強行要求\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You didn't ask, you demanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.08,0:28:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不允許自己被排除在外\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I will not be left out of the loop,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.92,0:28:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是總統的幕僚長\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm the president's chief of staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.65,0:28:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就這麼當幕僚長嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You call this being chief of staff?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.74,0:28:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,篡改他的日程安排\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Micromanaging his datebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.06,0:28:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如說是高階排程員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd say that's more of a glorified scheduler.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.45,0:28:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有我盡職盡責\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The White House would fall off its rails
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.33,0:28:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白宮會無法正常運作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}without me doing my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.35,0:28:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你確定嗎  -我確定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Are you certain about that? - Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.31,0:28:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我時刻為總統著想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I look out for the president 24/7.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.77,0:28:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓他知曉一切\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I keep him informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.97,0:28:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫他理清主次順序\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I keep his priorities straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.65,0:28:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當副總統前一切都好好的  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We did just fine before you became vice president, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.99,0:28:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我們現在就去總統辦公室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right, let's go over to the Oval Office right now
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.45,0:28:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓總統做個選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and ask the president to choose:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.71,0:28:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是幕僚長還是副總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}his chief of staff or his vice president.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.20,0:28:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他會選誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know what the answer would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.74,0:28:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要一起去嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.14,0:28:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你也不敢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.97,0:28:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明早要見到總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now I will see the president tomorrow morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.49,0:28:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管有沒有安排\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}schedule or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.68,0:28:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請離開前請把燈關上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And please, turn out the lights before you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.69,0:28:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你回家了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought you went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.46,0:29:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.64,0:29:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有空嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Um, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.15,0:29:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼問題嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.30,0:29:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在重新考慮建橋的事  我想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know you are reconsidering the bridge project and I want-
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.10,0:29:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在審查\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm reviewing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.01,0:29:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很快會決定的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll make my decision soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.14,0:29:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已經做出決定了  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you already made a decision, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.52,0:29:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心這事你是想多了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm concerned that you are overthinking this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.58,0:29:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-如果我們出爾反爾  -我沒說明白嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- If we backtrack... - Did I not make myself clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.14,0:29:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想表達我的看法  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm just trying to offer my advice, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.48,0:29:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經了解了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.26,0:29:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不用再聽第二遍了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And which I don't need to hear again
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.32,0:29:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but... thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.28,0:29:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道副總統昨天和你談過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know the vice president spoke to you yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.40,0:29:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平心而論\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and in fairness...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.02,0:29:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我重視你的想法  琳達\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know I value your input, linda,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.54,0:29:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說我已經了解了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but when I say I've heard it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.72,0:29:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是真的了解了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you need to know I mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.12,0:29:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.71,0:29:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有別的事嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is there anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.68,0:29:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒了  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.31,0:29:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-晚安  -晚安\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Good night. - Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.12,0:29:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我失望了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You disappointed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.98,0:29:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說了我需要時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I told you it would take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.69,0:29:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有線索嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Any leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.35,0:29:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在查他當州參議員時的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've been going over his state senate days.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.23,0:29:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這沒法快\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a slow process.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.78,0:29:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得徹底排查\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to be thorough.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.30,0:30:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼我兩天找到的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So how is it that i've found more in two days
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.01,0:30:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比你兩個月查到的還多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}than you have in two months?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.87,0:30:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.06,0:30:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還得替你完成差事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've had to do your job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.65,0:30:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有發現嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You found something?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.80,0:30:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是我來問你這個問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm the one who's supposed to ask that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.85,0:30:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你發現了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What'd you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.85,0:30:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說不定能幫忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe I can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.24,0:30:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在給弗蘭克幹活兒嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you working for Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.42,0:30:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我是他的媒體主管\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, as his communications director.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.15,0:30:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是問你在幫他收集情報嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, are you working for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.75,0:30:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.22,0:30:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給的錢比他能給的要多得多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He couldn't pay me a fraction of what you're offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.22,0:30:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別騙我了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.37,0:30:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你對我的能力沒信心了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, if you've lost confidence in my ability--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.28,0:30:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別他媽再唬我了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Stop fucking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.62,0:30:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的選擇是錯的  賽斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You made the wrong choice, Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.84,0:30:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.85,0:30:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼也不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.45,0:30:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是隻寄生蟲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're a parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.68,0:30:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一樣  丹頓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So are you Danton.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.50,0:30:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過更人模狗樣一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just in a nicer suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.75,0:30:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道可能是什麼嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you know what it might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.76,0:31:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意打聽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, keep your ear to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.30,0:31:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是賽斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That was Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.38,0:31:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他覺得雷米可能拿住了我們的把柄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He thinks Remy may have something on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.00,0:31:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.50,0:31:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.67,0:31:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你覺得可不可能是...  -不\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Do you think it could be-- - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.05,0:31:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算有  也肯定是無關痛癢的小事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If it's anything I'm sure it's innocuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.35,0:31:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們撐得住\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing we can't weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.84,0:31:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我猜  他們是在虛張聲勢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But my bet is they're bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.01,0:31:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過想嚇唬我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just to make us paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.01,0:31:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他是個危險的人  不是嗎  我是說雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But he's a dangerous man, isn't he? Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.26,0:31:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也可以很危險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can be dangerous too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.62,0:31:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果情勢需要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When we need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.13,0:31:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*主啊  情不自禁*\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}*Lord, I just can't*
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.13,0:31:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*偶爾灑淚*\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}*keep from crying sometimes.*
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.91,0:32:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*主啊  情不自禁*\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}*Lord, I just can't*
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.96,0:32:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*偶爾灑淚*\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}*keep from crying sometimes.*
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.12,0:32:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*世界充滿哀傷*\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}*When the world's filled with sorrow*
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.81,0:32:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*而我飽含熱淚*\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}*and my eyes are filled with tears.*
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.97,0:32:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*主啊  情不自禁*\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}*Lord, I just can't*
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.47,0:32:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,*偶爾灑淚*\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}*keep from crying sometimes.*
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.40,0:32:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別停\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.90,0:32:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經當過應召女郎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I used to be a call girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.82,0:32:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要逃離那種生活\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had to get away from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.48,0:32:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才來這裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that's why I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.89,0:32:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於我  你還有很多不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's a lot of stuff you don't know about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.60,0:32:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不想說  就什麼都不用說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't have to say anything you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.82,0:33:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在公交車上拍我肩膀的時候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When you tapped on my shoulder on the bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.77,0:33:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種感覺...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}there was something...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.46,0:33:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.33,0:33:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-這麼說真是太蠢了  -不\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- That sounds really, really dumb. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.52,0:33:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道怎麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Um, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.22,0:33:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想把一切都告訴你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I felt like I wanted to tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.43,0:33:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺得我能信任你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Like, that I could trust you,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.37,0:33:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-儘管與你素昧平生  -你可以信任我的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- even though I didn't know you. - You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.27,0:33:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒信任過任何人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I never trusted anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.66,0:33:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愛過別人嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Have you ever loved anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.97,0:33:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.72,0:33:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對這個世界沒什麼期望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've never expected much from the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.59,0:34:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得它很醜惡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.13,0:34:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是個公平的地方\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not a fair place.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.51,0:34:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對我現在擁有的很知足\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm happy to have what I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.97,0:34:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興我擁有現在\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm glad I have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.45,0:34:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都想清楚了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've thought it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.38,0:34:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種方式\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And there's a way to do it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.75,0:34:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有曝光的風險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so we don't risk any exposure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.63,0:34:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非要現在聊嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do we have to talk about this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.42,0:34:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我累了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.97,0:34:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的腦袋一團漿糊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My brain is f...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.72,0:35:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對  現在聊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.06,0:35:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是我們的婚姻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because it's our marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.44,0:35:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想要捱過接下來兩年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we're going to survive the next two years...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.22,0:35:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或六年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or six.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.62,0:35:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就得做點什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.07,0:35:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該互相支援\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We should be each others' support system.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.78,0:35:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是互相施壓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not cause each other stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.75,0:35:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白宮的基礎不是磚瓦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The foundation of this White House is not brick and mortar.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.50,0:35:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是我們啊  加勒特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's us, Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.09,0:35:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這對我很重要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.64,0:35:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你也能重視\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I want it to be important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.14,0:35:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得相信不管你在想什麼辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to trust that whatever you're managing,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.20,0:35:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你對我隱瞞了多少\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to whatever extent you choose not to inform me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.83,0:35:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既不會讓我有危險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that I'm neither at risk,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.01,0:35:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會讓我被動地縱容明顯的違法行為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}nor passively condoning something blatantly illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.72,0:35:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有風險都是我一人承擔\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Any risk solely falls on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.96,0:35:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知情  也不能被指責縱容\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you can't be accused of condoning what you're not aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.70,0:35:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知情也一樣糟糕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Being not aware is just as egregious.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.56,0:35:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這件事上不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.76,0:35:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在想辦法避開麻煩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm steering the ship away from the rocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.43,0:36:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是迎頭撞上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}not toward them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.94,0:36:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就給外資投資管理委員會打電話了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I'll call the committee for foreign investments.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.66,0:36:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的選擇很明智  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're making the right decision, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.75,0:36:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有個艱難的決定要做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have another difficult decision to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.31,0:36:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達提交了她的辭職信\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Linda submitted her resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.12,0:36:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很生她的氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was furious with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.83,0:36:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這招讓我很被動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That was a very manipulative move.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.77,0:36:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能猜到她為什麼這麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can speculate as to why she made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.96,0:36:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的不滿有道理嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are her complaints valid?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.76,0:36:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對這個問題的看法很主觀\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have a very biased view on that subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.32,0:36:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經聽過她的想法了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I've heard hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.80,0:36:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說說你的吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Give me yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.47,0:36:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達和我時不時會有爭執\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Linda and I don't always agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.56,0:36:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她對您忠心耿耿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But she's been very loyal to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.16,0:36:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一名非常得力的幕僚長\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and a more than competent Chief of Staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.86,0:36:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我該挽留她嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you think I should keep her?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.73,0:36:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得她有時會管太寬嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do I think she oversteps sometimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.79,0:36:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.73,0:36:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她錯以為自己的意見和我的一樣重要嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Does she wrongly equate her advice with mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.26,0:36:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常有的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Often.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.91,0:36:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我想到問題不在於琳達\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But... the question that occurs to me is not about Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.45,0:36:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你回絕了她的辭呈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's say you refuse her resignation,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.45,0:36:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,訊息很有可能傳出去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if this gets out, and it could,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.25,0:37:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣所有為你的工作的人  不是都會覺得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}won't you be sending a signal to anybody who works for you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.85,0:37:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們可以跟你談判\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...you can be leveraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.34,0:37:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她已經遞了辭呈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She offered her resignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.90,0:37:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便留下來心也不在這兒了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's already gone even if she stays.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.88,0:37:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根  他們準備好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Megan. They're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.62,0:37:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  我手一直在抖\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know, my hands are shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.18,0:37:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒問題的  梅根\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can do this, Megan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.41,0:37:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會在場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.72,0:37:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有時會恐慌發作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I get panic attacks sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.78,0:37:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你怕待會兒會發作嗎  -對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- You're afraid you'll get one? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.93,0:37:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  那我們再多等幾分鐘吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}OK, why don't we ask for a couple more minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.57,0:37:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不成問題  -不是時間的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- that's not a problem. - It's not about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.65,0:37:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐慌說來就來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}they just come.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.57,0:37:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無法控制\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.89,0:37:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想做了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.42,0:37:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根  屋裡面有很多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}OK, Megan, there's some of the most senior congressmen
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.45,0:37:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,資深國會議員\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and women in the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.38,0:37:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有媒體  他們專程為你而來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and the press, they've shown up just to hear from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.84,0:37:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.69,0:37:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我不想給你施壓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}OK, I don't want to pressure you,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.62,0:38:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們為了這個策劃了很久\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but a lot of planning has gone into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.95,0:38:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請別逼我做這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please don't make me do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.66,0:38:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不想逼你做什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're not making you do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.66,0:38:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我可以回家嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then can I just go back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.91,0:38:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-回芝加哥  -聽著  你緊張\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Back to Chicago? - Listen, you have nerves,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.80,0:38:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可以理解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that's understandable.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.63,0:38:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我他媽不想做了  好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't wanna fucking do it, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.48,0:38:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我理解你  沒關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I understand, it's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.88,0:38:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你要是現在退縮  梅根\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But if you back out now, Megan...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.14,0:38:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這根本不是為我  對吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This isn't about me at all, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.17,0:38:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我們會很不好  有損我們的形象\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}...this is not good for us. It hurts us,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.64,0:38:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓人覺得我們很鬆散\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it makes us look unorganized.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.47,0:38:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這他媽是你亮相的機會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is about your fucking moment to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.29,0:38:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本不在乎我怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't fucking care if do...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.92,0:38:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在乎  真心在乎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I do care. I do care.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.59,0:38:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了我  也是為了你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It is about me and about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.67,0:38:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是為什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And for whatever reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.95,0:38:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都說出了我們的經歷\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we both decided to share what happened to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.01,0:38:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人們在乎  人們願意傾聽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And it mattered and people listened
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.35,0:38:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們進去善始善終吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so let's go in and finish what we started.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.95,0:38:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到  我不合適\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't, I'm not the right person.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.99,0:38:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  梅根\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come on, Megan.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.68,0:38:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我昨晚做了什麼嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know what I did last night?
