Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.79,0:38:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不認識他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A total stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.22,0:38:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讓他在酒店裡瘋狂地幹我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I let him fuck my brains out at the hotel.
