Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.35,0:39:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.88,0:39:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你想要的代言人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not who you want to be your poster girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.29,0:39:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想的話就算了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.19,0:39:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想就算了吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't have to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.11,0:39:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉我讓你失望了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I'm letting you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.24,0:39:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  你沒讓我失望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's OK, you're not letting me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.64,0:39:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了  沒事的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's OK. It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.18,0:39:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候發表正式聲明\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When will it become official?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.64,0:39:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統今天下午就打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}President will make his call this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.76,0:39:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正式批准將在明天上午宣佈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Official approval will be announced in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.13,0:39:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,協議內容沒有改動吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No revisions to the agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.17,0:39:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  一切都寫在提案裡了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}None. Everything is as spelled out in the proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.28,0:39:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我會履行我的承諾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then I will uphold my end of the bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.38,0:39:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切斷資金流\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The money will be cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.34,0:39:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說要證據  現在我們也要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You required proof. Now we want some.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.51,0:39:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼證據\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.00,0:39:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的誠意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of your commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.46,0:39:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你終止和塔斯克的合作關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You kill your co-venture with Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.20,0:39:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們當初可沒說到這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That was never part of the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.73,0:39:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在說了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.20,0:39:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,貿易戰持續的話  精煉廠也運作不下去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The refinery can't proceed while we're in a trade war.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.31,0:39:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要你今後再不跟他合作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We want you to kill it for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.21,0:39:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且今天就辦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And we want you to kill it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.11,0:39:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給塔斯克打電話吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Make the call to Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.73,0:40:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是上班時間  要說公事嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's business hours. Is this a business call?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.09,0:40:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.91,0:40:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望不是公事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was hoping it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.78,0:40:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚有什麼安排嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are you doing tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.95,0:40:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上要上飛機了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just about to get on a plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.83,0:40:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到哪裡去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.74,0:40:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了分清界限嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Boundaries, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.10,0:40:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公事才有界限\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Work related.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.18,0:40:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是去度假\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't take vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.43,0:40:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候回來呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can you tell me when you'll be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.99,0:40:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天  很快就回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tomorrow. It's a quick trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.33,0:40:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想和我共進晚餐嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you want to have dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.84,0:40:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.13,0:40:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶上你的行李吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bring your carry-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.01,0:40:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃完飯順便過夜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can stay over after.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.12,0:40:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.05,0:40:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有空嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.96,0:40:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.02,0:40:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統一個小時前同意了我的辭呈\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The president accepted my resignation an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.39,0:40:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.47,0:40:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我差點說我改變心意了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I almost told him that I changed my mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.34,0:40:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我意識到沒有挽回餘地了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I realized it wouldn't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.27,0:40:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}For whatever it's worth,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.24,0:40:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提到了你的忠誠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I did bring up your loyalty
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.54,0:41:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及你出色的工作\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and how good you are at your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.12,0:41:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他並不需要我的提醒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not that he needed me to remind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.78,0:41:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你舉薦了我  我會一直心懷感激\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I will always be grateful you recommended me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.48,0:41:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這段路很精彩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It has been quite a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.17,0:41:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然比我想的短了一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Shorter than I would've hoped,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.50,0:41:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但還有大好前途等著我呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I have a long career ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.12,0:41:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.43,0:41:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想告訴你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.36,0:41:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想造成任何輿論風波\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't plan on making any fuss in the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.92,0:41:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人問  我一定都是溢美之辭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'll hear nothing but my praises if I'm asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.88,0:41:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有樣東西要給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.16,0:41:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾星期前\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A few weeks ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.89,0:41:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統跟我說起在你家的那頓晚飯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the president told me about a dinner he had at your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.55,0:41:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不停地說你的內戰模型\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He went on and on about your Civil War models.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.06,0:41:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還說跟你一起給玩具士兵上色可開心了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How much fun he had painting the toy soldiers with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.98,0:41:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是史密森尼的主管給我的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This was given to me by the director of the Smithsonian.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.98,0:41:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}位於美國華盛頓的一系列博物館和研究機構的集合組織
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.72,0:41:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是第一枚授予美籍西班牙人的榮譽勳章\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's the first Medal of Honor awarded to a Hispanic-American.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.08,0:41:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是授予約瑟夫·德·卡斯特羅下士的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Corporal Joseph De Castro.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.92,0:41:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他為聯邦作戰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He fought for the Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.01,0:41:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琳達  我不知道該說什麼好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Linda, I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.73,0:41:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很顯然總統把你當朋友看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's clear the president sees you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.16,0:41:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但沒把我當過朋友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've never been that to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.37,0:41:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他的工作超過友誼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But his job is bigger than friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.98,0:41:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我們倆都要重要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's bigger than you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.75,0:41:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能好好輔佐他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just hope you'll look out for him
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.29,0:41:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彌補我的遺憾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the way I've tried to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.14,0:41:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.42,0:41:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也會好好珍惜這枚勳章\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I'll treasure this.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.60,0:42:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見  副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Goodbye, Mr. Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.18,0:42:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從未像此刻這樣尊敬她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've never thought higher of her than I do at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.81,0:42:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她輸了  但她拼盡全力了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She lost, but she played to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.15,0:42:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德買通馮了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Underwood got to Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.27,0:42:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精煉廠沒戲了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The refinery's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.64,0:42:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,格雷森耍了我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Grayson played us.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.15,0:42:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們別無選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're running outta options.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.28,0:42:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼想  珍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you think, Jean?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.83,0:42:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去他的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Fuck him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.07,0:42:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.81,0:42:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.49,0:43:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的幫助  桑德拉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you for doing this, Sandra.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.20,0:43:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理查德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.19,0:43:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好嗎  理查德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How are you, Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.91,0:43:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的情況時好時壞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He has his good days and his bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.88,0:43:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天還不錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.33,0:43:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他希望在你結束後能和你聊聊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He'd love to spend a few minutes with you after your meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.71,0:43:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然可以\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.05,0:43:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牧師在裡面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The reverend's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.22,0:43:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沃剋夫人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.21,0:43:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.06,0:43:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.55,0:43:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牧師\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Reverend.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.22,0:43:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼可以效勞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.39,0:43:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得在這屋裡裝個電扇  弗蘭西斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You need to get a fan in here, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.80,0:43:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空調已經在全速運轉了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, the AC is all the way up to full blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.40,0:44:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說膠水的味道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I mean from the fumes, the glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.15,0:44:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也是樂趣的一部分嘛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, that's half the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.03,0:44:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根·漢納希今天臨陣退縮了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Megan Hennessy bailed on us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.82,0:44:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.43,0:44:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她太緊張了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Her nerves got to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.06,0:44:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她決定不在公眾面前露面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And she decided she didn't want to be in the public eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.98,0:44:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那倒也可以理解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, we can sympathize with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.56,0:44:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格的電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That was Doug.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.74,0:44:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.03,0:44:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Seth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.27,0:44:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒打給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.78,0:44:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When?
